        "summaries": {
          "bn": "নবী (সা.) পাঁচটি অনন্য বৈশিষ্ট্য উল্লেখ করেছেন।",
          "de": "Der Prophet (F) zählt fünf einzigartige Auszeichnungen auf, die ihm von Allah gewährt wurden.",
          "en": "The Prophet (SAWW), as narrated by Imam al-Baqir (AS), lists five unique distinctions given to him by Allah. These are foundational to Islamic law and theology: the universality of prayer locations, the permissibility of war spoils, divine support through fear cast into enemies' hearts, the gift of concise yet comprehensive speech, and the power of intercession on the Day of Judgment.",
          "es": "El Profeta (P) enumera cinco distinciones únicas otorgadas por Allah.",
          "fa": "پیامبر (ص) پنج امتیاز منحصر به فرد خود را بیان فرمود.",
